en: [List] 1846 Sept. 30 [List of Scholars in Pulaski, TN School District Number 3]
This document is a list of the scholars of the Pulaski, Tennessee School District, Number 3, as enrolled on September 30, 1846. There was a total of 35 scholars enrolled at that time.
